XAMPP Ldap module enable

To enable php ldap module in XAMPP, find the following files and copy them from C:\xampp\php to C:\Windows\system

01. libeay32.dll
02. libsasl.dll
03. ssleay32.dll

Edit your php.ini file which is located in C:\xampp\php and uncomment extension=php_ldap.dll around line 965.
Restart your apache server.

DLL files download link given below-
https://www.dropbox.com/s/g0r14utdqcssoow/XAMPP%20LDAP%20module%20dll%20files.zip?dl=0

Thants All
